title: Cafe Ambrosia
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Catering, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Specializing in Greek and Mediterranean cuisine. For vegetarians, the regular menu includes a veggie combo, a vegan combo, and a tofu combo platter, falafels & hummus, vegetarian sides, and make-your-own pasta option. On its website, menu page 7 is dedicated to "vegan and vegetarian specialties" and includes a vegan loaf, vegan mousaka, house vegan burger, charbroiled veggie wrap, tofu burrito, tofu and avocado wrap. For dessert a vegan apple loukomades. Staff will assist with veg diet requests - just ask.
